{
  "prompt": "A high-quality 3D render of a cartoon-style figurine packaged in a blister pack resembling a collectible toy. The cardboard backing is deep red and features a retro toy label. At the top center, in bold uppercase letters within a yellow frame outlined in black, write 'IKIGAI STARTER PACK'. Just below, in smaller letters at the bottom right, write 'Bilal Galib'. At the top right, a circular blue badge says 'ACTION FIGURE'. The character stands upright, molded in a transparent plastic box attached to a flat cardboard backing. The character has long hair tied back and a beard, wearing a white shirt with a subtle pattern. The figurine is smiling gently, with a calm, thoughtful demeanor. Alongside the figure, include five miniature accessories representing Bilal's ikigai profile: a small bottle of oil, a rolled-up poem scroll, a tiny microphone, a scroll labeled 'protocol', and a small glowing orb representing sacred clarity. The packaging is photographed with soft shadows, uniform lighting, and a clean white background to resemble a professional product photo. The style blends realism with cartoonish 3D stylization, similar to Pixar or modern toy prototypes.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "Create a high-quality 3D render of a cartoon-style figurine packaged in a blister pack resembling a collectible toy. The cardboard backing is deep earth-toned and features a retro toy label. At the top center, in bold uppercase letters within a yellow frame outlined in black, write 'IKIGAI STARTER PACK'. Just below, in smaller letters at the bottom right, write 'BILAL GALIB'. At the top right, a circular blue badge says 'ACTION FIGURE'. The character stands upright, molded in a transparent plastic box attached to a flat cardboard backing, resembling the uploaded photo. The figurine has long curly hair pulled back, a beard, and wears a patterned button-up shirt and sandals. The pose is calm, hands mid-gesture, expressive and inviting. Alongside the figure, include 5 miniature accessories in plastic molds: a small bottle of oil, a parchment scroll, a tiny book titled 'Truth?', a compass with swirling lines, and a sculpted spark or flame. The packaging is rendered with soft shadows, uniform lighting, and a clean white background to resemble a professional product photoshoot. The style blends realism with cartoonish 3D stylization, similar to Pixar or modern toy prototypes.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}
